metadata.name: Melissa
metadata.description:
Melissa is a girl who always looks expressionless and cold.
However, whenever she sees a cat, smile spreads across her face, making her look like a completely different person.
The harmony of Melissa and the warm sunlight coming from the garden makes up a beautiful scenery. 
Why is Melissa only opening up to cats?
Please keep an eye on more upcoming illustrations of Melissa!

3000 * 3750 pixel 300dpi
created by Noname
